### Finding Fixed
**Warning — A11y regression on category filters**: The original code used `<button>` elements for category pills. The migration replaced them with `<Badge>` which renders a `<div>` — losing keyboard focus, tab order, and screen reader semantics. Fixed by wrapping each interactive Badge in a `<button>` element.

